.TH TR300 1 "April 2026" "shaughvOS" "QubeTX 300 Series"
.SH NAME
tr300 \- QubeTX machine report (TR-300)
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B tr300
.RI [ OPTIONS ]
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B tr300
is the QubeTX TR-300 Machine Report. It prints a system summary
covering CPU, memory, disk, network, and operating system details.
.PP
By default, a full report is rendered. Use
.B \-\-fast
for a sub-second summary \- this is the variant shaughvOS runs
automatically at every terminal login.
.SH OPTIONS
See
.B tr300 \-\-help
for the full list of flags and modes.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR shaughvos (1),
.BR nd300 (1),
.BR sd300 (1),
.BR speedqx (1),
.BR autologin (1),
.BR desktop (1)
.SH AUTHOR
QubeTX \- a department of ES Development LLC.
Bundled with shaughvOS.
.SH HOMEPAGE
